            <title>[LU-13226] SUSE 15 SP2 server ldiskfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13226</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As it turns out the SLES 15 SP2 beta kernel can use the ldiskfs 5.4.7+ and later patch series directly.&lt;br/&gt;
 Update the lustre-build-ldiskfs.m4 to choose the 5.4 series file for SP2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is also true for the Ubuntu eoan 5.3 based kernel.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
